## audition

There are play and audition instances for:

  a) P (Event n)
  b) (String,P (Event n))
  c) P (String,Event n)

## fromList

> audition (pbind [("degree",pxrand 'a' [0,1,5,7] inf)
>                 ,("dur",fromList [0.1,0.2,0.1])])

There is a variant to make stopping patterns.

> audition (pbind [("degree",pxrand 'a' [0,1,5,7] inf)
>                 ,("dur",fromList' [0.1,0.2,0.1])])

