## pappend

Sequence two patterns.  This is the mappend instance of Monoid.

> fromList [1,2] `pappend` fromList [2,3]
> fromList [1,2] `mappend` fromList [2,3]
> ptake 5 (prepeat 3 `pappend` prepeat 4)
> ptake 5 (mconcat (cycle [prepeat 3]))
> let e = mempty :: P ()
> e `mappend` e == e

